{"tid":710690,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無手足試過坐巴士窗邊位 隔離條友唔肯讓比你落車","createTime":"2018-06-21T03:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T03:42:52.000Z","uid":32670,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"57e87e5b2be59bfc69857f8becebfabeaeb9b011","tid":710690,"uid":32670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T03:06:34.000Z","msg":"真人真事<br />\n是咁的 今朝搭巴士落車果陣 坐隔離條廢老地盤佬瞓著左 我就好有禮貌拍醒佢 講聲唔該 點知條廢老唔撚讓我出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我嬲到仆街 即刻用我兩隻腳轟埋去條廢老大脾到 嚇到條廢老即刻讓開比我出 然後我就頭也不回咁落下層落車 <br />\n走果陣仲見到坐我後面果個靚女OL用讚嘆既眼神望著我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好似想我做佢男朋友保護佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位手足平時撞到咁會點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004d052b4cd80a121f153a1a83b90b47bc3ba5b3","tid":710690,"uid":28831,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T03:07:50.000Z","msg":"未試過唔讓<br />\n好多仲會特登起埋身比我出<br />\n<br />\n是咪樓主個樣太柒太毒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451b662a3472baed88d4d703b66e049a054e0799","tid":710690,"uid":32670,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"004d052b4cd80a121f153a1a83b90b47bc3ba5b3","tid":710690,"uid":28831,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T03:07:50.000Z","msg":"未試過唔讓<br />\n好多仲會特登起埋身比我出<br />\n<br />\n是咪樓主個樣太柒太毒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T03:09:38.000Z","msg":"唔記得利申返<br />\n米8靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eaac6cbadfa2f074ebd95171c029afcb4044627","tid":710690,"uid":18167,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"451b662a3472baed88d4d703b66e049a054e0799","tid":710690,"uid":32670,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid